                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11">
                     <locus from="50ra" to="53ra"/>
                     <title type="complete">Prayers and readings for the deseased when the grave is being digged.
                       The text includes excerpts Ronams 6; ///from <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3516Epistle"/> 15:23-39; <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3507Epistle"/> 3:15 - 4:11;
                          <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1019Actsof"/> 7:55 - 8:2; an antiphon (<foreign xml:lang="gez">kǝśtat</foreign>) for the deacons;
                          <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1693John"/> 12:20-26; the prayer after the gospel and the prayer of the penance.</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቀዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ሶበ፡
                        ይመውት፡ ሰብእ፡ እንዘ፡ ይከርዩ፡ ግበ፡ ፫፡ ጊዜ፡ ፫፡ ወተአተብ፡ ገጸከ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ስረዩ፡ ላዕለየ፡ ሊተ፡ አበውየ፡ ወአሐውየ፨ ጸልዩ፡ ሊተ፡ <sic resp="DN">እስነአለክሙ፡</sic> በጸሎትየ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለአብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቀዱስ፡
                        ይእዜኒ፡ ወዘልፈኒ፡ ወለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፨ አሜን፨
                     </explicit>
                     </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.12">
